            "stanza_text": "Les concetti du crépuscule\nFrisaient les bouquets de nos seins ;\nSon haleine encore y circule,\nEt, leur félinant le satin,\nFait s'y pâmer deux renoncules."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Devant ce Maître Hypnotiseur ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Expirent leurs frou-frou poseurs ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Elles crispent leurs étamines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et se rinfiltrent leurs parfums",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Avec des mines",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
