                    "line_text": "Noués de faveurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! Ah !\nIl neige des cœurs\nNoués de faveurs,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Reviens, vagir parmi mes cheveux, mes cheveux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Tièdes, je t'y ferai des bracelets d'aveux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Reviens, vagir parmi mes cheveux, mes cheveux\nTièdes, je t'y ferai des bracelets d'aveux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Entends partout les Encensoirs les plus célestes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+4+4",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "L'Univers te garde une note unique ! Reste…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8+4",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Entends partout les Encensoirs les plus célestes,\nL'Univers te garde une note unique ! Reste…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "C'est le nid meublé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Par l'homme idolâtre ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Les vents déclassés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Des mois près de l'âtre ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Rien de passager,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Presque pas de scènes ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "La vie est si saine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Quand on sait s'arranger.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Ô fiancé probe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Commandons ma robe !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Hélas ! Le bonheur est là, mais lui se dérobe…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est le nid meublé\nPar l'homme idolâtre ;\nLes vents déclassés\nDes mois près de l'âtre ;\nRien de passager,\nPresque pas de scènes ;\nLa vie est si saine,\nQuand on sait s'arranger.\nÔ fiancé probe,\nCommandons ma robe !\nHélas ! Le bonheur est là, mais lui se dérobe…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Bestiole à chignon, Nécessaire divin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Os de chatte, corps de lierre, chef-d'œuvre vain !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bestiole à chignon, Nécessaire divin,\nOs de chatte, corps de lierre, chef-d'œuvre vain !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Ô femme, mammifère à chignon, ô fétiche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "On t'absout ; c'est un Dieu qui par tes yeux nous triche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ô femme, mammifère à chignon, ô fétiche,\nOn t'absout ; c'est un Dieu qui par tes yeux nous triche,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Beau commis voyageur, d'une Maison là-haut,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Tes yeux mentent ! Ils ne nous diront pas le Mot !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Beau commis voyageur, d'une Maison là-haut,\nTes yeux mentent ! Ils ne nous diront pas le Mot !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Et tes pudeurs ne sont que des passes réflexes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Dont joue un Dieu très fort (Ministère des sexes).",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et tes pudeurs ne sont que des passes réflexes\nDont joue un Dieu très fort (Ministère des sexes)."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 16,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Tu peux donc nous mener au Mirage béant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Feu-follet connu, vertugadin du Néant ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "12",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tu peux donc nous mener au Mirage béant,\nFeu-follet connu, vertugadin du Néant ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 17,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Mais, fausse sœur, fausse humaine, fausse mortelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Nous t'écartèlerons de honte sensuelles !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, fausse sœur, fausse humaine, fausse mortelle,\nNous t'écartèlerons de honte sensuelles !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 18,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Et si ta dignité se cabre ? À deux genoux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Nous te fermerons la bouche avec des bijoux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et si ta dignité se cabre ? À deux genoux,\nNous te fermerons la bouche avec des bijoux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 19,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "‒ Vie ou Néant ! Choisir. Ah ! Quelle discipline !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Que n'est-il un Éden entre ces deux usines ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Vie ou Néant ! Choisir. Ah ! Quelle discipline !\nQue n'est-il un Éden entre ces deux usines ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 20,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Bon ; que tes doigts sentimentals",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Aient pour nos fronts au teint d'épave",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Des condoléances qui lavent",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Et des trouvailles d'animal.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bon ; que tes doigts sentimentals\nAient pour nos fronts au teint d'épave\nDes condoléances qui lavent\nEt des trouvailles d'animal."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 21,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Et qu'à jamais ainsi tu ailles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Le long des étouffants dortoirs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Égrenant les bonnes semailles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "En inclinant ta chaste taille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Sur les sujets de tes devoirs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et qu'à jamais ainsi tu ailles,\nLe long des étouffants dortoirs,\nÉgrenant les bonnes semailles,\nEn inclinant ta chaste taille\nSur les sujets de tes devoirs."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 22,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! Pour une âme trop tanguée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Tes baisers sont des potions",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Qui la laissent là, bien droguée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Et s'oubliant à te voir gaie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Accomplissant tes fonctions",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "En point narquoise Déléguée.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! Pour une âme trop tanguée,\nTes baisers sont des potions\nQui la laissent là, bien droguée,\nEt s'oubliant à te voir gaie,\nAccomplissant tes fonctions\nEn point narquoise Déléguée."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 23,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Des ramiers",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Familiers",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Sous nos jupes palpitent !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Doux Çakya, venez vite",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Les faire prisonniers !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Des ramiers\nFamiliers\nSous nos jupes palpitent !\nDoux Çakya, venez vite\nLes faire prisonniers !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 24,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Défaillantes, les Étoiles, que la lumière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "12",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Épuise, battent plus faiblement des paupières.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Défaillantes, les Étoiles, que la lumière\nÉpuise, battent plus faiblement des paupières."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 25,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Le ver-luisant s'éteint à bout, l'Être pâmé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Agonise à tâtons et se meurt à jamais.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le ver-luisant s'éteint à bout, l'Être pâmé\nAgonise à tâtons et se meurt à jamais."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 26,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Et l'Idéal égrène en ses mains fugitives",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
